---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageTitle from '../components/PageTitle.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="COA Policy | Peptide Shop"
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: "Home", url: "/" },
    { name: "COA Policy", url: "/coa-policy" }
  ]}
>
  <PageTitle 
    title="Certificate of Analysis (COA) Policy"
    subtitle="Our commitment to transparency and quality documentation."
    breadcrumbs={[
      { name: "Home", url: "/" },
      { name: "COA Policy" }
    ]}
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
          <p class="lead mb-4">At PeptideResearch.eu, we believe in complete transparency regarding the quality of our reagents.</p>

          <h2 class="mt-4 mb-3">Batch-Specific Testing</h2>
          <p>Every batch of peptide we manufacture undergoes rigorous testing before it is released for sale. We do not rely on "generic" COAs. The COA you download corresponds to the current batch in stock.</p>

          <h2 class="mt-4 mb-3">Verification Methods</h2>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li class="mb-2 d-flex align-items-start"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mr-2 mt-1 text-color flex-shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg><span><strong>HPLC (High-Performance Liquid Chromatography):</strong> Used to quantify purity and identify impurities.</span></li>
            <li class="mb-2 d-flex align-items-start"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mr-2 mt-1 text-color flex-shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg><span><strong>MS (Mass Spectrometry):</strong> Used to confirm the molecular mass and identity of the peptide.</span></li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="mt-4 mb-3">Availability</h2>
          <p>Digital copies (PDF) of COAs are available for download directly from each product page. If you require a hard copy or raw data files for your records, please contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
